summary:
"It is only with the heart that one can see rightly; what is essential is invisible to the eye." The Little Prince

Born an optimist in a small town in the middle of somewhere, I felt an urge to seek out freedom and adventure early on in life in travel, work and ventures. Following my heart and passion led me to try out many different jobs for sometimes short periods of time and both failing and succeeding many small business ideas. Besides meeting a lot of wonderful people every single endeavour helped me find out the following key things about myself:
